1cd887f06e113a59e350762d1e89","tid":928704,"uid":33104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T09:17:01.000Z","msg":"見到個名諗起「布布」"},{"pid":"f9ed19a200caba4384dfff4b68db05170cd43bbd","tid":928704,"uid":32527,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:27:15.000Z","msg":"唔講佢份人<br />\n佢咁有心成日拍戲真係算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7500946699271f31a6021e95e601a734b40efb6d","tid":928704,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:40:40.000Z","msg":"另外據片方向我們介紹，電影將蒲松齡設定為屢破奇案的&ldquo;鬼狐居士&rdquo;，同時妖的形象和個性也更加多樣，期間穿插了多個故事，也融入了不同角色之間的情感糾葛，這樣的改編不僅增加了故事的新鮮感，也擴寬了&ldquo;聊齋&rdquo;本身的意義。<br />\n<br />\n電影《神探蒲松齡之蘭若仙踪》在著力刻畫蒲松齡這個人物形象的同時，將故事地點聚焦在&ldquo;蘭若寺&rdquo;，它出自《聊齋誌異》中《聶小倩》的故事，幾乎是鬼域的代名詞。但&ldquo;仙踪&rdquo;兩字又讓電影多了幾分美麗，這種美不僅體現在場景畫面，更凸顯了主角之間交織著愛恨糾纏的曠世之戀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a167c5874e677fbb32950b082b8062d1d1c0bd51","tid":928704,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:44:17.000Z","msg":"感覺好金瓶梅feel"},{"pid":"681d4cf02bf1b5b9b34322774fc65e3ff4fc6fd3","tid":928704,"uid":33456,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:44:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/f/f8/Digimonq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Ff%2Ff8%2FDigimonq.gif&h=0c53c9f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"885ca6894eba4ca9d9c7a5ed569148745782e771","tid":928704,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:16:05.000Z","msg":"有套卡通叫成龍傳奇 仲膠"},{"pid":"f533129347bd5e99953993551caf0f283c233285","tid":928704,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T01:47:58.000Z","msg":"法國做親蒲松齡嘅都係仆街<br />\n代表啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}